subject: Booking Confirmed — {{ customer_name }}
<h2>Booking Confirmed!</h2>
<p>Dear {{ customer_name }},</p>
<p>Your bike rental booking has been confirmed.</p>
<table>
  <tr><td><strong>Booking ID:</strong></td><td>{{ booking_id }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Hub:</strong></td><td>{{ hub_name }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Bike Model:</strong></td><td>{{ model_name }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Start:</strong></td><td>{{ start_date }} {{ start_time }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>End:</strong></td><td>{{ end_date }} {{ end_time }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Total Amount:</strong></td><td>{{ amount }}</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Please arrive at the hub at least 15 minutes before your rental starts for check-out.</p>
<p>Thank you for choosing {{ hub_name }}!</p>
